[I] AI powered Kubernetes Assistant

[T] kubectl-ai acts as an intelligent interface, translating user intent into
[T] precise Kubernetes operations, making Kubernetes management more accessible
[T] and efficient.

[U] https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/kubectl-ai

[A] Google Inc.
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool

[E] add kubectl

[L] APL
[V] 0.0.30

[D] 1a16360a4180a9dc82b399170e151d9a8560b0f8f6bee3de26370855 kubectl-ai-0.0.30.tar.gz https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/kubectl-ai/archive/v0.0.30/

